<pageBreakToken pageId="6" pageNumber="77" start="start">Local</pageBreakToken>
name.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="6" pageNumber="77">Karawek Phruksa Sawan.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="77" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="6" pageNumber="77">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="6" pageNumber="77">The fruit and seeds are only known from fresh material and have not been preserved due to fungal infection.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="6" pageNumber="77">
The distinction between 
<taxonomicName class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Annonaceae" genus="A." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. spathulatus" order="Magnoliales" pageId="6" pageNumber="77" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="spathulatus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">A. spathulatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Annonaceae" genus="A." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. tanaosriensis" order="Magnoliales" pageId="6" pageNumber="77" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="tanaosriensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">A. tanaosriensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is corroborated by unpublished phylogenetic analysis of combined chloroplast (
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">matK</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">ndhF</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">psbA-trnH</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">trnL-F</emphasis>
) and nuclear (
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">AP3</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">carboxymethylenebutenolidase</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">GI</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">HMGS</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">LFY</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">mag1</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">ncpGS</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">NIA</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">PhyA</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">RPB2</emphasis>
) DNA sequence data, which retrieved 
<taxonomicName class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Annonaceae" genus="A." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. spathulatus" order="Magnoliales" pageId="6" pageNumber="77" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="spathulatus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">A. spathulatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as sister to 
<taxonomicName class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Annonaceae" genus="A." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. uniflorus" order="Magnoliales" pageId="6" pageNumber="77" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="uniflorus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">A. uniflorus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, with 
<taxonomicName class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Annonaceae" genus="A." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. tanaosriensis" order="Magnoliales" pageId="6" pageNumber="77" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="tanaosriensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">A. tanaosriensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sister to 
<taxonomicName class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Annonaceae" genus="A." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. suaveolens" order="Magnoliales" pageId="6" pageNumber="77" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="suaveolens">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="77">A. suaveolens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(J. Chen et al. unpublished data).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
